<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='489000' id='t-489000'>but it's the four R's, rather than the three R's --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='492000' id='t-492000'>then I think we're going to be on our way.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='494000' id='t-494000'>So these three are not perfect -- they're ideas.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='497000' id='t-497000'>I think that there are many problems to come,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='500000' id='t-500000'>but with help, I'm sure I'm going to find solutions.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='503000' id='t-503000'>And I hope you all take part.</span>
</span>
</p>
